import React from 'react'
import { Nav, NavbarContainer, Navlogo } from './NavbarElements'


const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    // putting fragments to avoid a bunch of divs
    <>
    <Nav>
        <NavbarContainer>
            <Navlogo to='/'>NaVak</Navlogo>
            <MobileIcon>
              <FaBars/>
            </MobileIcon>
            <NavMenu>
              <NavItem></NavItem>
            </NavMenu>
        </NavbarContainer>
    </Nav>
    </>
  )
}

export default Navbar;
